!!【词语辨析】

:<div>

----------------------------------------

        ↓ insist, persist 的辨析 ↓         

----------------------------------------

insist >> 坚持，后面接介词on，也可直接连用that引导的名词从句。如：He insisted on my going there with him. (He insisted that I should go there with him.)

persist >> 坚持，后面常接介词in。如：He persisted in carrying on his work in spite of great fatigue.(他虽然疲倦极了，可仍坚持工作。)

</div>

